summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing acceptance from the Washington State Transportation Commission of Franchise No. 2872 and 2997 for the construction, operation and maintenance of sanitary sewers in certain portions of P.S.H. No. 1 (I-5), from Northeast 143rd Street to vicinity Northeast 155th Street, and in portions of P.S.H. No. 2-80 (Bothell Way Northeast) between northeast 150th Street and Northeast 170th Street.
